1a3e6b9b5cebb66f2e04896a7b316f9d4d20cb4709f16cb56" style=3D"text-decoration=
:underline;color:#d40000;">Vuori gear</a> had become inescapable. Nearly ev=
ery other parent on the sidelines was wearing their hoodies, outerwear, or =
ubiquitous joggers. Their tech pants, which dominate the post-pandemic offi=
ce casual scene alongside <a href=3D"https://email.puck.news/e/c/eyJlbWFpbF=
9pZCI6ImRnVDJ4Z1lEQUt2UktxclJLZ0dVaXhwb2stdExweC1YNDVUQlIxdz0iLCJocmVmIjoia=
HR0cHM6Ly9nby5zaG9wbXkudXMvcC0xMjIzNzI0Mz91dG1fY2FtcGFpZ249TGluZStTaGVldCst=
K1NVQlNDUklCRVJTKyUyODElMkYyMSUyRjI1JTI5XHUwMDI2dXRtX2NvbnRlbnQ9TGluZStTaGV=
ldCstK1NVQlNDUklCRVJTKyUyODElMkYyMSUyRjI1JTI5XHUwMDI2dXRtX21lZGl1bT1lbWFpbF=
